<br>
Just for good measure, he watched as one of his chosen mortal warlords rode alongside Fogstone and prepared for battle with his warriors.  The cupbearer Ganymede was among the warlord's mortal followers.  Zeus smiled as he watched the boy then thought for a moment how the boy looked out of place on the battlefield.  <br>
<br>
